sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as Data Science Pipelines<br/>(DSP Orchestrator)
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant UI as Kubeflow Pipelines UI

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Metadata Recording

    DSP->>MLMD: PutArtifactType / PutExecutionType<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS/mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE type schemas<br/>MySQL/PG protocol, Optional SSL<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    DB-->>MLMD: Type IDs
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutArtifactTypeResponse

    DSP->>MLMD: PutExecution<br/>(execution + artifacts + events atomically)
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT execution, artifacts, events<br/>Single transaction
    DB-->>MLMD: Stored
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutExecutionResponse

    DSP->>MLMD: PutAttributionsAndAssociations<br/>(link contexts to artifacts/executions)
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT attributions, associations
    DB-->>MLMD: Stored
    MLMD-->>DSP: Response

    Note over UI,DB: Flow 2: Lineage Query

    UI->>MLMD: GetLineageSubgraph<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT with graph traversal<br/>(direction, hops, filters)
    DB-->>MLMD: Lineage nodes and edges
    MLMD-->>UI: LineageSubgraph response<br/>(artifacts, executions, contexts, events)

    UI->>MLMD: GetArtifactsByContext<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT artifacts WHERE context_id=?
    DB-->>MLMD: Artifact records
    MLMD-->>UI: Artifacts for visualization

    Note over MLMD,DB: Note: Connection-per-RPC pattern<br/>No connection pooling (b/123039345)
